<paragraph id="8BFD36D5860F6B29FA9B847EF833F7AA" blockId="29.[1299,2286,1781,2281]" box="[1347,1961,2058,2097]" pageId="29" pageNumber="92">Geological age. Late Tournaisian.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFD36D5860F6B29FA9A844DFA38F716" blockId="29.[1299,2286,1781,2281]" pageId="29" pageNumber="92">Etymology. Referring to the microspiral ornamentation of shell.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFD36D5860F6B29FA9A84E1F72BF772" blockId="29.[1299,2286,1781,2281]" pageId="29" pageNumber="92">Remarks. This form is characterised by densely spaced fine spiral lirae and a deviated protoconch.</paragraph>
